    "chemicalDescription": [
      "sr-(Pentapeptide-107 Hexapeptide-40 sh-Polypeptide-164) is a single chain fusion peptide, produced by fermentation in E. coli. The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from Pentapeptide-107 and sh-Polypeptide-164. The fusion peptide contains 179 amino acids which may contain disulfide bonds and/or glycosylation, and consists of the proper sequence from the 20 standard amino acids."
